ions</span></li>
 </ul>
 <p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Manrope;font-size:16.0pt'><span
 style=3D'font-weight:bold'>Q5. What is Amazon VPC?</span></p>
 <p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Manrope;font-size:11.0pt'>Amazon VPC en=
ables
 users to establish isolated network environments in AWS by setting up IP
