 <p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Manrope;font-size:16.0pt'><span
 style=3D'font-weight:bold'>Q6. What is AWS Lambda?</span></p>
 <p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Manrope;font-size:11.0pt'>AWS Lambda ex=
ecutes
